| `前端接线` | Fast short CJK title/file recall |
| `尼帕病毒` | Short CJK recall across chat and files |
| `四源搜索` | Short CJK recall across directory/file records |
| `自然语言 本体论` | CJK phrase recall with heading/body evidence |
